{"tid":1251553,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如果想買一本出左好耐既冷門書應該點搵","createTime":"2019-06-22T14:42:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T11:37:09.000Z","uid":126889,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3973e7bdf914b5ad450a17642c94b98aec3f6256","tid":1251553,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T14:42:43.000Z","msg":"本書叫二開 有漫畫加小說既作品 漫畫部分係出自利志達<br />\n<br />\n以前中學迫人訂報紙 唔知係咪信報通識 有一排佢最尾果版一定有個故仔睇 好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nD同學一食飯就拎一份報紙拎墊台 但我就專草埋幾期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來本書一次過收錄左上面講既故仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n商務個網有本書既資料但冇寫存貨資料 本書2011出 我諗都好難搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n公共圖書館又冇<br />\n有冇巴打一樣試過想搵本出左好耐既冷門書 如果我打去出版社度會唔會有得諗?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c2fd616bbefce61cfc61dbd79bb646cba864f9","tid":1251553,"uid":208196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T05:21:21.000Z","msg":"去搵個作者"},{"pid":"a46ca61818ba573dcf46f98252388ff62883d9e3","tid":1251553,"uid":126889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"37c2fd616bbefce61cfc61dbd79bb646cba864f9","tid":1251553,"uid":208196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T05:21:21.000Z","msg":"去搵個作者"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T11:22:32.000Z","msg":"講實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？ 咁我試試先"},{"pid":"f9f49053ece402231040e6d7feb3f7d2dd633ee7","tid":1251553,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T11:37:09.000Z","msg":"打去書局問"}]}